Since 1999 we have been the Austrian partner organisation in the global Friends of the Earth network. Friends of the Earth Europe unites more than 30 national organisations with thousands of local groups and is part of the world's largest grassroots environmental network, Friends of the Earth International.&#xd;
&#xd;
GLOBAL 2000 is also member of several other networks, for a list please refer to: https://www.global2000.at/strategische-partnerschaften
